OL,7,FWatch Rags Martel's report
OL,9,FGovernment ministers have said "no
OL,10,Fchild should suffer as Ella did" as
OL,11,Fthey settled a legal case over the
OL,12,Fdeath of a schoolgirl who died from an
OL,13,Fair pollution-linked asthma attack.
OL,15,FMPs told her mother they are "truly
OL,16,Fsorry for your loss," in a statement
OL,17,Fat a meeting today ahead of a High
OL,18,FCourt battle.
