OL,3,CMinisters apologise to mother of girl
OL,4,Cwho died after air pollution asthma
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FElla Adoo-Kissi-Debrah, a nine-year-
OL,8,Fold from south-east London, suffered a
OL,9,Ffatal asthma attack in February 2013
OL,10,Fafter being exposed to excessive air
OL,11,Fpollution.
OL,13,FIn a landmark coroner's case in 2020,
OL,14,FElla ` who had lived 25 metres from
OL,15,Fthe busy South Circular Road in
OL,16,FLewisham ` became first person to have
OL,17,Fair pollution listed as a cause of
OL,18,Fdeath at an inquest in the UK.
