OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIt marked the culmination of a long
OL,8,Fbattle by Ella's mother, Rosamund Adoo-
OL,9,FKissi-Debrah, to have the role of air
OL,10,Fpollution in her daughter's death
OL,11,Frecognised.
OL,13,FHer late daughter's estate, over which
OL,14,FMs Adoo-Kissi-Debrah acts as
OL,15,Fadministrator, sued the Environment
OL,16,FDepartment (Defra), the Department for
OL,17,FTransport and the Department for
OL,18,FHealth and Social Care, for
OL,19,Fcompensation over Ella's "illness and
OL,20,Fpremature death".
