OL,7,FThe three government departments have
OL,8,Fsettled the claim ahead of a High
OL,9,FCourt trial for an undisclosed sum.
OL,11,FA statement issued to Ms Adoo-Kissi-
OL,12,FDebrah on behalf of the three
OL,13,Fdepartments said the government was
OL,14,F"truly sorry for your loss" and
OL,15,Fexpressed sincere condolences to her,
OL,16,FElla's siblings and everyone who knew
OL,17,Fher.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@[O]
