OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe statement from ministers of the
OL,8,Fthree departments acknowledged that
OL,9,F"no child should suffer as Ella did"
OL,10,Fand said: "To lose a loved one at such
OL,11,Fa young age is an immeasurable loss."
OL,13,F"The tireless work undertaken by
OL,14,FElla's family and friends over the
OL,15,Fyears, in particular by you, her
OL,16,Fmother, has shone a much-needed
OL,17,Fspotlight on the dangers posed by air
OL,18,Fpollution.
