OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"Air pollution is a public health
OL,8,Fissue that this Government is
OL,9,Fcommitted to tackling," the statement
OL,10,Fsaid, adding that Ms Adoo-Kissi-Debrah
OL,11,Fhad helped to ensure the issue was
OL,12,Ffirmly on the Government's agenda.
OL,14,FAir Quality Minister Emma Hardy said:
OL,15,F"By working together in the years to
OL,16,Fcome, more can be achieved in
OL,17,Fimproving not only the quality of the
OL,18,Fair we breathe but also in raising
OL,19,Fawareness of the health implications
OL,20,Fof air pollution."
