OL,7,FAs the letter was released, Ms Adoo-
OL,8,FKissi-Debrah, along with Ella's
OL,9,Fsiblings, met with environment
OL,10,Fminister Emma Hardy at the Defra
OL,11,Foffices in London.
OL,13,FThe meeting is part of the settlement
OL,14,Fof a civil claim brought by law firm
OL,15,FHodge Jones & Allen of Ella's estate
OL,16,Fagainst the three government
OL,17,Fdepartments for breaches of Ella's
OL,18,Frights under the Human Rights Act,
OL,19,Fincluding her right to life.
